Incandescent blue sphere

Curse:
You feel strongly compelled to action.
You are impatient, unable to hold still, fidgety, and prone to impulsive actions.
+4 Initiative
-4 Stealth
Unable to delay or ready an action.

DC20 Will save to rest.
Failure = Unable to gain any benefit from resting.  No HP regain, no spell renewals, etc.


Boon:
This stone grants the wearer a +2 enhancement bonus to Wisdom.



